data.description: What's not to love? On the outer fringe of New Albany lies this quiet neighborhood. Spacious brick home has been so nicely updated! Open layout, floods of natural light, beautiful finishes and on an oversized wooded lot. Check out this beautiful kitchen with Maple (real wood) cabinets, granite counter and stainless appliances, which all stay. Great bedroom sizes on both levels feature new carpet and freshly painted. The owners suite is ginormous with dual closets and luxurious modern bathroom. The FINISHED WALKOUT BASEMENT features a family/game room w/ 2nd fireplace (which is only decorative), full bath, 4th bedroom, laundry and oversized 2c garage. What beautiful views out the back!  NO HOMES behind the backyard, just woods. The yard is fenced and the chicken coops stay (for people who embrace a self sustaining mindset).  There is a tremendous amount of living space here and so close to amenities. NEW: entire HVAC system, roof, skylights, picket fence, chimney cap, fireplace insert, not to mention the kit/baths which were updated 5yrs ago. The home sits on a DOUBLE LOT.
